    }

you are incrementing the variable by 16 and not 15. So remove `count1++ + 15` and make it `count1 + 15`. You may also use shorthand operator `+=`.

    public void scoreCount() {
        count1 = count1 + 15;
    }

OR

    public void scoreCount() {
